sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant API
    participant UserService
    participant UserModel

    User->>API: POST /users/register (Invalid Email)
    API->>UserService: register_user(user_data)
    UserService->>UserModel: validate(user_data)
    UserModel-->>UserService: ValidationError ("Invalid email format")
    UserService-->>API: raise error
    API-->>User: 400 Bad Request ("Invalid email address")
